checkDatesAndTimes(LocalDateTime, LocalDateTime) - Method in class controller.Controller
This method checks the "from" date and time and the "to" date and time to see if there are problems.
A message will be shown to the user in these scenarios: "from" date and time is after the "to" date and time "from" date and time is placed in the future
